  6→ * Smart default:
  7→ *   deus              On a desktop → launch app (install if needed)
  8→ *                     On a server  → start headless with web UI
  9→ *
 10→ * Explicit commands:
 11→ *   deus serve        Start headless server with web UI
 12→ *   deus desktop      Download and install the desktop app
 13→ */
